{# A tool-result <details> collapsible.

   The label / body come from ToolDisplayConfig.format_result; results
   that the config returns ``None`` for are suppressed at the Task
   level and don't reach this template.

   Body is wrapped in <pre> so whitespace is preserved (file contents,
   prover output, etc.) and CSS can scroll it independently of the
   surrounding panel.

   ctx:
     label  — short result title (autoescaped)
     body   — full result body (autoescaped, pre-formatted)
#}
<details class="tool-result">
  <summary class="tool-result-summary">{{ label }}</summary>
  <pre class="tool-result-body">{{ body }}</pre>
</details>
